patients receiving EBR/GZR, NoTx, and pegIFN/RBV. EBR/GZR was estimated to 
extend life expectancy by 4.2 and 2.0 years compared with NoTx and pegIFN/RBV.
CONCLUSIONS: Our model predicted that EBR/GZR will significantly reduce the 
incidence of liver-related complications and prolong life in patients with 
